Writing LATEX docs

Linux
Install texlive packages
sudo apt-get install texlive-...

Install one Latex editor
- kile: sudo apt-get install kile
- texmaker: sudo apt-get install texmaker


Windows
Install MikTex package. See the link below:
http://www.miktex.org/2.9/setup

Install one Latex editor:
- TexMaker: http://www.xm1math.net/texmaker/index.html
- TexnikCenter: http://www.texniccenter.org/

Latex Docs
http://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/LaTeX

